Permanens Capital :: Permanens :: Welcome

























Our TeamHow we investContact Us




Permanens Capital is a boutique asset management firm that provides custom, outsourced investment solutions for endowments, foundations, and family offices. Through our open architecture investment platform, the firm currently oversees approximately $2.6 billion across multiple asset classes for institutional investors.Permanens was formed in 2011 with assets from its principals and a fully outsourced university endowment. The firm’s partners and senior professionals have substantial buy-side investment expertise as well as extensive experience with endowment management and non-profit board governance. Our “peers as service providers” approach to OCIO services is highly differentiated from other providers due to the executive team’s experience as both direct investors and nonprofit trustees.




