Company Overview of Permanens Capital L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Permanens Capital L.P. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative markets. It also invests in exchange traded funds. The firm uses external research to make its investments. Permanens Capital L.P. was founded in June 2011 and is based in New York City.


